    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>I've migrated my personal library to namespaces and I've detected that the namespaced prefix paths are not properly handled by the plugin loader because both Zend_Form and Zend_Form_Element add "_$type" as suffix to the plugin path when they should detect if the namespace separator is _ or \</p>

